# Summary
Microscope is a feature in Amplitude that allows users to analyze specific data points in charts by hovering over them, providing options like viewing user streams, showing user paths, creating cohorts, and integrating with features like Session Replay, Feature Flags, and Guides/Surveys based on the selected data point.

